PACKAGE INFO
Textmate Bundles for OpenErp
Snippets are meant to be used with Openerp 5 or later

There are 2 Bundles in this package: OpenerpXML and OpenerpPy. 
OpenerpXML allows you to easily create Openerp XML Data files and fill them by useful snippets for records, views, workflows, etc.
OpenerpPy has been made to make your life simpler when developing osv models, wizards, etc.

INSTALLATION
Just copy the *.tmbundle files into your ~/Library/Application\ Support/TextMate/Bundles/ directory, and reload bundles. That's it!
